    h1 Toolbar React Component
    ul.docsIndex
    p Toolbar is a fixed (with Fixed and Through layout types) area at the bottom of a screen that contains navigation elements. Toolbar does not have any parts, just plain links inside
    p Toolbar React component represents <a href="../docs/toolbar-tabbar.html">Toolbar</a> component.

    h2 Toolbar Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li `Toolbar` / `F7Toolbar`

    h2 Toolbar Properties
    table.params-table
      thead
        tr
          th Prop
          th Type
          th Default
          th Description
      tbody
        tr
          th(colspan="4") &lt;Toolbar&gt; properties
        tr
          td inner
          td boolean
          td true
          td When enabled (by default), it will put all the content within internal `toolbarInner` element. Disable it only in case you want to put totally custom layout inside
        tr
          td position
          td string
          td
          td #[a(href="/docs/toolbar-tabbar.html#toolbar-position") Toolbar position], can be `top` or `bottom`
        tr
          td top
          td boolean
          td
          td Top positioned toolbar. Shortening for `position="top"`
        tr
          td topIos
          td boolean
          td
          td Top positioned toolbar only for iOS theme
        tr
          td topMd
          td boolean
          td
          td Top positioned toolbar only for MD theme
        tr
          td topAurora
          td boolean
          td
          td Top positioned toolbar only for Aurora theme
        tr
          td bottom
          td boolean
          td
          td Bottom positioned toolbar. Shortening for `position="bottom"`
        tr
          td bottomIos
          td boolean
          td
          td Bottom positioned toolbar only for iOS theme
        tr
          td bottomMd
          td boolean
          td
          td Bottom positioned toolbar only for MD theme
        tr
          td bottomAurora
          td boolean
          td
          td Bottom positioned toolbar only for Aurora theme
        tr
          td tabbar
          td boolean
          td false
          td Defines whether the Toolbar is also a Tabbar or not
        tr
          td labels
          td boolean
          td false
          td Enables Tabbar with labels (affects only when `tabbar: true`)
        tr
          td scrollable
          td boolean
          td false
          td Enables scrollable Tabbar (affects only when `tabbar: true`)
        tr
          td noShadow
          td boolean
          td
          td Disable shadow rendering for Material theme
        tr
          td noHairline
          td boolean
          td false
          td Disable toolbar/tabbar top thin border (hairline) for iOS theme
        tr
          td hidden
          td boolean
          td false
